CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 1, 1967, pg. 14 reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Maurice H. McCall - Harris photo. Portions of accompanying article reads: "The Mt. Olive Baptist Church of this city was the scene of the recent wedding of Donna W. Dalton and Maurice H. McCall...The double-ring ceremony was performed by the Rev. Brannon J. Hopson, pastor of the bride, assisted by the Rev. Charles Foggie, the groom's pastor of Wesley Centre AME Zion Church, Pittsburgh."
TitMainTitle: Groom Maurice McCall wearing light colored dinner jacket, and bride Donna W. Dalton McCall wearing gown with lace sleeves and train, posed in Mt. Olive Baptist Church, Rankin
